data.title: Mad for Each Other
data.text: Funniest show of the year. Highly recommended. Human beings are so funy.

data.title: I shall go outside again one day
data.text: This pretty much sums up my year.

data.title: House of Dragon
data.text: The blonde thing is a bit strange but I still believe redemption+ for the last season is still possible! Let's go dragons~~ Dracarys!!!

data.title: Squid Game
data.text: This almost made me tear for some reason. Was it the context, narration or strategy? This was done so well.

data.title: Arcane
data.text: Fantastic series. Music is ON POINT. The game is also great but they need to quit nerfing Xerath - he's squishy enough, godammit.

data.title: Imposter Syndrome vs. Dunning Kruger Effect
data.text: Maybe it's good to give yourself credit sometimes, no matter what others think. Look what I can do!!

data.title: BillieSpeaks
data.text: Animals are sentient. They do have thoughts and feelings. I wish everyone were aware and mindful of this.

data.title: Imposter Syndrome
data.text: Feels like there's #*@% everywhere. Everything smells like #*@%. Bob Saget is underrated.
